    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Eriteus">Heriteo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone
                            memorie Ermitei</persName> permuta beni con <persName ref="#people/3305"
                            key="#Bishops">[Hiere]mias</persName> gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…). Eriteo cede ad parte
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/292" key="#Churches">Sancti Mihaelis arcangelis,
                            sita infra hanc Lucanam civitatem ad Foro</orgName>, id est una <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">petia de terra mea</rs>, qua[s abeo
                        in] <placeName ref="#places/166" key="#Confinia">Tempaniano</placeName>, qui
                            <rs key="#Confinia">uno caput tenet</rs> in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, alio caput in terra q[………], lato uno tene in terra mea (…)
                        et alio lato tene in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> suprascipte
                        ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/292" key="#Confinia">Sancti
                            Mihaelis</orgName>. Predicta petia de terra (…) est per mensura ad iusta
                        pertichas mensurata <rs key="#Size">sistariorum quatuordecim</rs> (…).
                        Riceve in cambio una <rs key="#Curtes #Petiae #Landed_possessions">petiola
                            de terra quod […] curte</rs>, seo terra vacua in suprascripto loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/166"
                            key="#Confinia #Curtes #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads #Queen"
                            >Tempaniano</placeName>, prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Churches">Sancte Marie</orgName>, pertinentes
                        predic[te ecclesie vestre] Sancti Mihaelis archangelis, et est tenentes ipsa
                        terra uno caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput [tenet] <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Queen">[i]n vinea domne
                            regine</rs> et ambas lateras est tenentes in orto et vinea sive curte
                        mea qui sopra Heritei. Et petia ipsa de curte et orto sive terra (…) est per
                        mensura ad iusta pertichas mensurata <rs key="#Size">sistariorum octo et
                            schalas tres</rs> (…). Ubi et super hanc comutationem tu qui supra
                            <persName ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops">H[ieremias</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>] [di]rexisti <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Bishops">missos vestros</rs>,
                        id est <persName key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Deacons"
                                ><name>Teusprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Subdeacons"
                                ><name>Sichalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs>, et <persName ref="#people/1514"
                            key="#Marquis/duke">Adalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs>
                        <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">mi[sso suo</rs> id est
                            <persName key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName>] filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedicti</name> de <placeName ref="#places/703"
                                >Versiciano</placeName></persName>, qui ambulaverunt cum alios bonos
                        et credentes homines (…). Pena in duplum. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Rofredus">Roffridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Oltre ai missi sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                        Uilipertu, Teufridi scabinus, Adalghisi, Lampertus, Georgius notarius,
                        Teudimundo. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
